              "<p>Several months after the man I love broke up with me, I had a moment of vivid realization as I looked at my dog, Trucker, curled up on my bed. His eyes were slightly open, he looked sad, and all morning he had periodically looked out the front windows of our home as if he was waiting for someone. &#8230;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.dogster.com/lifestyle/my-dog-is-mourning-my-ex-and-it-breaks-my-heart\">My Dog Is Mourning My Ex, and It Breaks My Heart</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.dogster.com\">Dogster</a>.</p>\n"
